# Email Configuration untuk System TA
# Salin konfigurasi ini ke file .env Anda

# ===== MAIL CONFIGURATION =====
MAIL_MAILER=smtp
MAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
MAIL_PORT=587
MAIL_USERNAME=your-email@gmail.com
MAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password
MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=your-email@gmail.com
MAIL_FROM_NAME="${APP_NAME}"

# ===== UNTUK GMAIL =====
# 1. Enable 2-Step Verification di akun Google
# 2. Buat App Password di https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
# 3. Gunakan App Password sebagai MAIL_PASSWORD

